record_data.record_plain_text:
PARKWAY GENERATION KEYS ENERGY CENTER LLC Reactive Supply and Voltage Control from Generation Sources Service Parkway Generation Keys Energy Center LLC ("Parkway Gen Keys") provides Reactive Supply and Voltage Control from Generation Sources Service ("Reactive Supply Service") from a generating facility located in Prince George's County, Maryland to the PJM Interconnection, L.L.C. ("PJM") system. This Rate Schedule sets forth Parkway Gen Keys' revenue requirement for the provision of Reactive Service from the facility pursuant to Schedule 2 of the PJM Open Access Transmission Tariff, which provides for PJM to pay generation owners their monthly revenue requirements for Reactive Service.
This Rate Schedule shall be effective upon the date authorized by the Federal Energy Regulatory Commission.
REVENUE REQUIREMENT Total Annual Revenue Requirement is $4,063,008. Total Monthly Revenue Requirement is $338,584.
